The people of Adamawa have been congratulated on their choice of Dr. Mahmood Halilu Ahmad, a scholar, thoroughbred, community builder and distinguished academic, as Sarki Gabas Adamawa. Prince Oyedamola Diya, the Chairman of Dforte integrated Global Nigeria Limited and Executive Director, Pilot Finance Ltd gave the commendation in a statement made available to Daily Independent in Lagos. Prince Diya, in the statement, described the new Sarki Gabas Adamawa, Dr. Ahmad as a jolly good fellow, a selfless, honest and hard-working gentleman, whose meritorious service tothe community and humanity are unparalleled. -Advertisement- Diya, a coursemate and associate of the new traditional ruler stated: “I celebrate an achiever, a brother and dear friend, Dr Mahmood Halilu Ahmad on his turbaning as the Sarki Gabas Adamawa” “You were my neighbour and also worked together on an assignment during a critical assignment where you displayed uncommon leadership, dedication and resourcefulness to ensure we delivered on our mandate.The statement added, “You are a born leader blessed with an infectious simplicity. I have no doubt whatsoever that you are the man whom the cap fits to provide the leadership and direction needed by the great people of Adamawa, and indeed Nigeria.Congratulations.” Besides, Prince Diya wished the new Sarki Gabas Adamawa a happy and peaceful reign as he ascends the throne of his ancestors. However, true to Prince Diya’s accolades about the Sarki Gabas Adamawa, his subjects have similarly described him as a seasoned and dynamic leader. They said his generosity is iconic, his love for the younger generation legendary, his passion for the preservation of progressive customs and traditions practice unparalleled, his mentoring ability exceptional and his love for the overwhelming.